And Jadeja, 25, was found to have been complicit in the incident.

Anderson will find out if he too will be punished for the incident during his personal ICC hearing which takes place on Friday, August 1.

India lead the series 1-0 following a 95-run victory at Lord's in the second Test. 

The third Test begins at the Rose Bowl in Hampshire on Sunday.  

